  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Update on PROJECT CARS 3. All product sales will end on: August 24th, 2025 23:59 UTC. Please note that times may vary by region. If you bought the game digitally it will remain in your library and can be redownloaded in the future. Any DLCs purchased before August 24th, 2025 23:59 UTC will still be available to use after this date. The game’s online modes will also remain active until February 24th, 2026.]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/958400/extras/044b1d215bcff835b750a900a076ec02.poster.avif?t=1756079735\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/958400/extras/044b1d215bcff835b750a900a076ec02.webm?t=1756079735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/958400/extras/044b1d215bcff835b750a900a076ec02.mp4?t=1756079735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OWN YOUR JOURNEY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t200+ elite-brand race & road cars </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t120+ global tracks </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tWide set of race conversion kits</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tRace to earn Credits & XP </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tBuy & own 100s of cars </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tUpgrade cars with realistic performance parts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tCustomize your car liveries with racing- & community-inspired elements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tPersonalize your drivers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FEEL EACH MOMENT</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tFully scalable assists for all skill levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tConvincing & fun handling</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t24-hour cycle, dynamic all-seasons, all-weather racing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tUnrivalled Controller Experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tVisceral sense of speed </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tIntense crash effects & car-contact </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tEnhanced AI </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EARN EVERY WIN</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tNew & deeply engaging career mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tBattle your way up from weekend warrior to racing legend</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tNew & compelling Multiplayer and Community Modes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tFun & exciting Daily Challenges</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/958400/extras/46cbdcafe87f5239162bd7e837a67dc7.poster.avif?t=1756079735\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/958400/extras/46cbdcafe87f5239162bd7e837a67dc7.webm?t=1756079735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/958400/extras/46cbdcafe87f5239162bd7e837a67dc7.mp4?t=1756079735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
